rows.label: qst300304_msg0001
rows.name: Are you the leader?

rows.label: qst300304_msg0002
rows.name: No, the leader is this young man here.

rows.label: qst300304_msg0005
rows.name:
You're a very young leader, but...
[ML:Dash ]you're very trusted. I like that.

rows.label: qst300304_msg0006
rows.name: I'm Fisena. From Superbia.

rows.label: qst300304_msg0007
rows.name: Is there anything you'd like to ask?

rows.label: qst300304_msg0051
rows.name: What should I ask?

rows.label: qst300304_msg0052
rows.name: Motivation

rows.label: qst300304_msg0053
rows.name: Skills

rows.label: qst300304_msg0054
rows.name: Future goals

rows.label: qst300304_msg0055
rows.name: Nothing in particular

rows.label: qst300304_msg0101
rows.name:
I was looking for work,
wandering from place to place,

rows.label: qst300304_msg0102
rows.name:
and I heard that the
reputation of this Hr√¶svelgr
Merc Group is excellent.

rows.label: qst300304_msg0103
rows.name:
I can't fight...[ML:Dash ] but I thought
I could help those who do.

rows.label: qst300304_msg0104
rows.name: I feel like there's another reason.

rows.label: qst300304_msg0105
rows.name:
[ML:Dash ]There was nothing fun
for me in Alba Margen.

rows.label: qst300304_msg0106
rows.name:
Everyone had a grim face and
seemed busy...[ML:Dash ] I didn't like
that, so I left Superbia.

rows.label: qst300304_msg0201
rows.name: I don't have anything in particular...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst300304_msg0202
rows.name:
but if I had to say, it would
be my positive attitude.

rows.label: qst300304_msg0203
rows.name: That's a really good thing.

rows.label: qst300304_msg0204
rows.name:
Hehe...[ML:Dash ] thank you. I'm
happy to hear that.

rows.label: qst300304_msg0205
rows.name:
That's right. Also, I can make dishes
that go well with alcohol! The best
moment is a drink after work.

rows.label: qst300304_msg0301
rows.name:
I don't think about difficult
things like the future.

rows.label: qst300304_msg0302
rows.name:
If today is fun, that's enough. I
believe that if today is fun,
tomorrow will surely be fun too.

rows.label: qst300304_msg0303
rows.name: Is that just about yourself?

rows.label: qst300304_msg0304
rows.name:
No, that's not it. It would
be lonely if only I were
having fun, wouldn't it?

rows.label: qst300304_msg0305
rows.name:
I will spare no effort to make
everyone around me happy.

rows.label: qst300304_msg0401
rows.name: This concludes the interview.

rows.label: qst300304_msg0402
rows.name:
We will inform you of the
results later. You may go.

rows.label: qst300304_msg0403
rows.name: I see. I'm hoping for a good result.

rows.label: qst300304_msg0404
rows.name: Now, I'll call the next candidate.

rows.label: qst300304_msg0501
rows.name:
Is there anything else
you'd like to ask?
